  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <note><para>If you need a plugin for a given dependency, that dependency
      needs to be installed before this application.
    </para></note>

    <para>
      Suppress installation of unnecessary files:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed "s/ install-data-local//" -i docs/plugins/Makefile.in</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Prepare the package for compilation:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix= \
            --disable-nls</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Compile the package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make -j1 install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

